Kesse!

706
01:24:19,920 --> 01:24:22,161
What's up?

707
01:24:24,760 --> 01:24:27,286
I just wanted to check in on you.

708
01:24:27,520 --> 01:24:29,807
I'm not talking. Don't worry.

709
01:24:30,000 --> 01:24:35,086
- Who tipped the inspectors?
- I have no idea.

710
01:24:36,920 --> 01:24:41,084
I'll find out who it was.
Someone owes me a wee favor.

711
01:24:41,280 --> 01:24:44,682
It doesn't matter anymore.

712
01:24:52,920 --> 01:24:56,641
- We had a good business going.
- What do you want?

713
01:25:00,240 --> 01:25:02,925
I'll pay that fine.

714
01:25:03,160 --> 01:25:07,245
When you get your license back
we'll slowly settle the account.

715
01:25:07,440 --> 01:25:12,651
You'll get your boat and quotas back.
Everything will be as before.

716
01:25:12,800 --> 01:25:15,963
I think you need to go now.

717
01:25:20,520 --> 01:25:24,286
- Think about it.
- I've thought about it.

718
01:25:24,440 --> 01:25:27,091
Think about it.

719
01:25:27,240 --> 01:25:30,323
I've thought about it.

720
01:25:30,520 --> 01:25:32,807
Goodbye, Carsten.

721
01:25:46,280 --> 01:25:50,604
What's up? Are you coming
to fisherman's swim tonight?

722
01:25:50,800 --> 01:25:57,160
- Why? I'm not a fisherman anymore.
- Stop that. Neither am I.

723
01:25:57,360 --> 01:26:00,887
Did you hear about Lars?
He got beat up.

724
01:26:01,080 --> 01:26:04,482
- That wouldn't be a first.
- No, a proper beating.

725
01:26:04,640 --> 01:26:06,881
Some say it was hired goons.

726
01:26:09,120 --> 01:26:11,964
- What the hell did he do?
- I don't know.

727
01:26:12,200 --> 01:26:17,366
I met Inga at the supermarket.
She was shook up and crying.

728
01:26:17,560 --> 01:26:21,121
Hey! Where are you going? Kesse!

729
01:26:26,120 --> 01:26:29,169
Did you tip the inspection? Huh?

730
01:26:31,040 --> 01:26:35,887
Did you?
Do you even know what you did?!

731
01:26:36,080 --> 01:26:40,529
- You had it coming!
- Did I? Did I really?

732
01:26:40,720 --> 01:26:45,044
Kesse! Leave him alone.

733
01:27:04,440 --> 01:27:07,489
- So ...
- Take care.

734
01:27:07,680 --> 01:27:10,160
Thanks.

735
01:27:19,440 --> 01:27:23,604
- Put it down for a second.
- Just step down.

736
01:27:23,800 --> 01:27:25,768
- No.
- You're a wimp.

737
01:27:25,960 --> 01:27:29,282
Go on.

738
01:27:43,040 --> 01:27:46,806
Hello, Pia. Just the usual.

739
01:27:50,200 --> 01:27:53,409
- Hello.
- Hi.

740
01:27:54,960 --> 01:27:57,611
- It's been a while.
- Yes.

741
01:27:58,880 --> 01:28:03,568
- Are you doing okay?
- Just fine.

742
01:28:03,720 --> 01:28:07,486
I'm working at the fish factory.
I get benefits and all.

743
01:28:07,680 --> 01:28:11,924
So that's all good.

744
01:28:12,160 --> 01:28:14,686
- What about you?
- Fine.

745
01:28:17,000 --> 01:28:21,881
- How did the project go?
- Good. It's done.

746
01:28:22,040 --> 01:28:26,409
- Well, congratulations then.
- Thanks.

747
01:28:29,600 --> 01:28:32,365
- I'm going back to Copenhagen.
- Oh.

748
01:28:32,520 --> 01:28:36,127
- When are you leaving?
- At 4 o'clock.

749
01:28:36,320 --> 01:28:39,642
- Today?
- Yes.

750
01:28:47,040 --> 01:28:51,045
- Bye, Kesse.
- Bye. Do you need a ride?

751
01:28:51,240 --> 01:28:53,971
- What?
- How will you get to the airport?

752
01:28:54,160 --> 01:28:57,369
I can borrow Sorte's car
and take you there.

753
01:28:57,520 --> 01:29:02,765
- I'm taking the train.
- Oh, okay.

754
01:29:02,960 --> 01:29:06,521
Then it's ...

755
01:29:09,160 --> 01:29:12,482
- Bye.
- Bye.

756
01:29:20,880 --> 01:29:24,726
- At least we got rid of her.
- Huh?

757
01:29:24,920 --> 01:29:30,324
It's not that I just think,
she was a bit too pushy.

758
01:29:31,760 --> 01:29:36,209
A bit too aggressive. Right?

759
01:29:36,400 --> 01:29:42,521
Maybe it's because she's from
Copenhagen. We're not like that.

760
01:29:44,360 --> 01:29:47,443
Don't you think?

761
01:31:07,760 --> 01:31:12,721
<i>This is Gerd. I can't come to the
phone. Please leave a message.</i>

762
01:32:01,800 --> 01:32:04,041
- Can I buy a ticket here?
- Sure.

763
01:32:04,240 --> 01:32:08,404
- Where are you going?
- I'm going to Copenhagen.

764
01:32:45,080 --> 01:32:49,005
Subtitles: Christa Hejlstrup
SDI Media Denmark

